job.title: HAL Trade Technician Recruitment 2021  Apply online for Various Vacancies in Lucknow
job.body:
Total Vacancies: Various

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Trade Technician

Description

Latest Central Government Jobs for ITI diploma holders have been published by Hindustan Aeronautics Limited for Trade Technician vacancies in Lucknow. If you are searching for a government job in Lucknow then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Trade Technician, from 18.06.2021., and till 18.06.2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Lucknow and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • No information about application fee

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for a Trade Technician  in HAL, your ITI must be completed from a recognized Institution

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 18.06.2021.
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 18.06.2021

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 18 to 27 years old. 

HAL Trade Technician Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary

is 9000 per month

How to apply for HAL Trade Technician Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Trade Technician. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of HAL and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by HAL.
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.

Download Official notification pdf.
